<p style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:8pt;\">- Poker engine for the popular &quot;Texas Hold'em&quot; Poker</span></p>
